{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"event.relatedTarget","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/relatedTarget","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/altKey\"><code>altKey</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/button\"><code>button</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/buttons\"><code>buttons</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/clientX\"><code>clientX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/clientY\"><code>clientY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/ctrlKey\"><code>ctrlKey</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/layerX\"><code>layerX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/layerY\"><code>layerY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/metaKey\"><code>metaKey</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/movementX\"><code>movementX</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/movementY\"><code>movementY</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/mozInputSource\"><code>mozInputSource</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetX\"><code>offsetX</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/offsetY\"><code>offsetY</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageX\"><code>pageX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageY\"><code>pageY</code></a></li><li><em><code>relatedTarget</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenX\"><code>screenX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/screenY\"><code>screenY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/shiftKey\"><code>shiftKey</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/WEBKIT_FORCE_AT_FORCE_MOUSE_DOWN\"><code>WEBKIT_FORCE_AT_FORCE_MOUSE_DOWN</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/WEBKIT_FORCE_AT_MOUSE_DOWN\"><code>WEBKIT_FORCE_AT_MOUSE_DOWN</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/webkitForce\"><code>webkitForce</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/x\"><code>x</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/y\"><code>y</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/getModifierState\"><code>getModifierState()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/initMouseEvent\"><code>initMouseEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Wskazuje na drugi cel zdarzenia.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">eventTarget = event.relatedTarget\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>eventTarget</code> to referencja do dodatkowego celu zdarzenia (obiektu <code>EventTarget</code>).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var rel = event.relatedTarget;\n// dump(\"LEAVING \" + (rel&nbsp;? rel.localName&nbsp;: \"null\") + \"\\n\");\n// relatedTarget is null when the titletip is first shown:\n// a mouseout event fires because the mouse is exiting\n// the main window and entering the titletip \"window\".\n// relatedTarget is also null when the mouse exits the main\n// window completely, so count how many times relatedTarget\n// was null after titletip is first shown and hide popup\n// the 2nd time\nif (!rel) {\n  ++this._mouseOutCount;\n  if (this._mouseOutCount &gt; 1)\n    this.hidePopup();\n  return;\n}\n// find out if the node we are entering is one of our\n// anonymous children\nwhile (rel) {\n  if (rel == this)\n    break;\n  rel.parentNode;\n}\n// if the entered node is not a descendant of ours, hide\n// the tooltip\nif (rel&nbsp;!= this &amp;&amp; this._isMouseOver) {\n  this.hidePopup();\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Za specyfikacją W3C: \"Obecnie ten atrybuty używany jest przy zdarzeniu <a href=\"pl/DOM/element.onmouseover\">mouseover</a>, gdzie kieruje do <code>EventTarget</code>, jaki opuściło urządzenie wskazujące oraz przy zdarzeniu <a href=\"pl/DOM/element.onmouseout\">mouseout</a>, gdzie kieruje do EventTarget, w który weszło urządzenie wskazujące.\"</p>\n<p>Powyzszy przykład jest typowy - właściwość <b>relatedTarget</b> używana jest by znaleźć, jeśli jest związany z tym zdarzeniem, kolejny element. Zdarzenia takie jak najechanie myszą (\n <i>\n  mouseover</i>\n ) są powiązane z konkretnym elementem docelowym, ale mogą też angażować drugi cel, jak np. element opuszczany przez mysz w momencie, gdy najechania na główny cel.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Events-20001113/events.html#Events-MouseEvent-relatedTarget\" rel=\" noopener\">relatedTarget </a></p>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Wskazuje na drugi cel zdarzenia.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MouseEvent.relatedTarget","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MouseEvent.relatedTarget","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MouseEvent.relatedTarget","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/mouseevent/relatedtarget","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/mouseevent/relatedtarget/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/relatedTarget","title":"event.relatedTarget"}],"pageTitle":"event.relatedTarget - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}